               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184308210126"></xptr>
               <p>from a man's pocket—I took him, and with one of his hands he pulled out this other handkerchief—the other four dropped from him on the way to the station—he said he bought them in Petticoat-lane—the gentleman would not give his name.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was going to look at the procession, and this man took me.</p>
